"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Contacts</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"在<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">聯絡人</font></strong>應用程式，可儲"
"存藝術家、捐贈者、合作夥伴等的聯絡資料。"

#. module: museum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:museum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Store location details (e.g., <em>Gallery C – Permanent Collection</em>) and "
"include notes like <em>“Display on pedestal, under soft light.\" </em>on "
"\"<em>Description for Receipts field</em>\"."
msgstr ""
"儲存詳細位置資訊（例如：畫廊 C － 常設館藏），並在「收據描述」欄位中加入註"
"釋，例如：置於底座上，在柔和燈光下展示。<em></em><em></em><em></em>"

#. module: museum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:museum.contactus
